{"tid":1394664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8.3 西洋菜街登打士街要人！！！","createTime":"2019-08-01T13:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T15:35:42.000Z","uid":209337,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bdf03892675a05bf8a8b7892e74ed684c59f19ac","tid":1394664,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:20:24.000Z","msg":"8.3 西洋菜街登打士街要人！！！<br />\n<br />\n發夢見到8.3星期六好多人去旺角行街，不過上次7.7有班黑警阻住大家行街，仲反包圍毆打市民，佢老母星期六肯定大把重兵埋伏亂咁打人，而家班黑警可以射催淚彈上老人院，真係有咩做唔出，所以出去行街真係萬事小心！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">✔ 登打士街</span><br />\n唔計彌敦道，登打士街有成5個出口位，邊度行邊度走由你話事，萬一畀狗追，仲可以向華仁衛理道方向避一避。<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警唔撚怕打人，但如果連廣華醫院都夠膽放催淚彈嘅話，咪撚話全城憤怒，畀CNN影到再全球報導，聯合國都要出聲譴責，迫撚到林奠要開獨立調查委員會！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">✔ 西洋菜(南)街</span><br />\n西洋菜街行街好正常，又可以去百老匯、新寶睇吓戲，仲可以幫襯樓上舖振興經濟。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">✖亞皆老街（旺角東方向）</span></span><br />\n咪以為行大街就冇事，唔好唔記得先達隔籬大把仆街潮聯（自己上網搵就明）。畀你走到又點？行上火車站方向多數都要靠接駁天橋，萬一有狗block哂條路，隨時比人反包圍，更加唔洗諗新世紀對出d巴士(可能改道)。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">✖旺角道天橋</span><br />\n天橋去火車站只能單一方向走，又係隨時比狗圍死，除非到時仲有出口比你落金魚街或者出番彌敦道去始創，否則可免則免，想走隔離有旺角站B2 /B3出口，過對面A1/A2出口走又一條好漢。<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eqMVKWf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeqMVKWf.png&h=1f15202e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZtsqnH4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZtsqnH4.png&h=60c9adbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n齊上齊落 不撤不散<br />\n8月3日，旺角見！！<br />\n<br />\n8.5 全港大罷工 七區集會"},{"pid":"504d80e1a03459e9f598f4d88786427273af82f2","tid":1394664,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:20:41.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"b366b4be3e2e9361f6abeb0b99428510de812182","tid":1394664,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:20:52.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"39d3137c79ed798410eaac72867a4c5c1d22adab","tid":1394664,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:21:09.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"553bac1ee88c021fab2daec5f1a047fbac0cf7e0","tid":1394664,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:21:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69eed3755e58142b20cf50db1ecdc9f05e91f4ac","tid":1394664,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:22:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7be4342ebcfd3dc9a28595688c073c190480ae9f","tid":1394664,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:22:22.000Z","msg":"推～"},{"pid":"1d6c18d1b10b4394365d3aded9c2424faddaa7fc","tid":1394664,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ceguoK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ceguoK.png&h=8390e925&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dtOH9oN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdtOH9oN.png&h=c2484d95&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97RCdQv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97RCdQv.png&h=1f593e10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26063df09c873ed18029517db2cd19ee8456bf3e","tid":1394664,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:23:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1fd359f1a1e71d7e8e75f06e94759afcfec257c1","tid":1394664,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:24:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5cbd1cb87359f1356328097311e3417fd7dd0942","tid":1394664,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:24:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d3699a3e273ed9ee74a24322f3498b63d7651a5e","tid":1394664,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:24:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0c899b0e5af43987847d921943df20f0889e98